{"tid":2509387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"VA Wong Sir網上畫政治漫畫遭教局裁定專業失德投訴成立 未來教席或不保","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:43:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e564f7643c1c29b6d563e342d9f65fc65f4283","tid":2509387,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖繼續籠罩教育界，於社交媒體創作政治漫畫的中學教師「vawongsir」（黃Sir）今（29日）在其個人社交媒體上表示，去年被匿名投訴指其漫畫「不恰當」，最終教育局裁定為專業失德投訴成立，而判詞中更諷刺地寫及「漫畫對政府或警察提出『無理』指控，例如法治已死、警黑勾結」。<br />\n<br />\n自2019年5月始，於網上發表政治漫畫的黃Sir，去年有人匿名向教育局投訴，指他於社交平台專頁所創作的政治漫畫為「不恰當」，教育局不滿意他的解釋，去信校董會，其後黃被當時任教的大埔聖公會莫壽增會督中學以「資金不足」不被續約。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwYnGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=599ae79a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M%2F&h=cdded0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M/</a>"},{"pid":"1fe48874702102a10b081a378c5b0b89d98fcffa","tid":2509387,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5304c918e6484470d133c07ef66741f6544ec6d8","tid":2509387,"uid":137704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"兩間龍頭MST可以同監獄鬥仆街"},{"pid":"896aaec3aed1c6605309df8abc41430c5cb119cf","tid":2509387,"uid":315798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"大家like咗黃sir個專頁未呀？<br />\n未嘅就快啲去like啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8933425